---
title: Sweet & Smokey Pork Loin Steaks with Creamy Bacon Potatoes & Apple Salad
description: This is no ordinary pork loin steak! Seasoned with our smokey Kiwi spice blend and coated in sweet onion chutney, it’s got incomparable flavour. Add a side of creamy potatoes speckled with crispy bacon and you’ve got a truly unbeatable meal.
